## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of recent studies and data, as some sources may not reflect the latest trends in art education. Additionally, the findings are based on a selection of articles and may not encompass all perspectives on the subject. Further research could include more diverse sources and longitudinal studies to provide a comprehensive view of the long-term benefits of art education for children.